> vt run test # cache miss
$ vtt print-file test.txt
initial content
> vtt mkdir -p subfolder

> vtt cp test.txt subfolder/test.txt

> vtt replace-file-content vite-task.json '"cache": true' '"cache": true, "cwd": "subfolder"' # change cwd

> vt run test # cache miss: cwd changed
~/subfolder$ vtt print-file test.txt ○ cache miss: working directory changed, executing
initial content
